    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @lkbr, thanks for sharing your feedback. \r\n\r\nIf I recall correctly we are putting the selected values at the top even for the Menu to make sure they're going to appear. \r\n\r\nLet's say the user find a category that has a count under all those already displayed, the selected category will not appear if the sort is only on count:desc because the limit will be applied. \r\n\r\nWhat would be the behaviour you would have expect on that case? Having an extra category displayed? ",
