    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The behavior is inconsistent with other flavors (no other flavor has a searchable `<Menu>` but it's the same with `<RefinementList>`). Keeping the order when the menu is searchable is not perfect but that's what we defaulted to. We might at least want to be consistent.",
